    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1895-09-06T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1895-09-06T00:00:00-05:00" n="386"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d386">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Adee</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Armstrong</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1895-09-06">
                            <hi rend="italic">September 6, 1895</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Telegraph when you have answered Spanish minister’s note. Reservation indicated
                    in my telegram of 24th ultimo touching currency and place of payment apparently
                    obviated by later understanding. If any qualification now appears telegraph it
                    clearly.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Adee</hi>, <hi rend="italic">Acting.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
